Secure boot

- secure boot code
- validate program with it's own key
- prevent malware from launching at boot time

Secure boot or restricted boot ?

- enable/disable secure boot.
- run prgoram's doesn't have certificate key.
- can't install os doesn't have certificate key.

solution to install linux

- choose a linux distribution that support secure boot
- add a key to the UEFI firmware
- disable secure boot

boot from flash

- disable fast boot
- disable windows fast startup feature
- disable CSM

dual boot

- it seem's user can install linux and windows 10 inside together

